Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Heart Of Dra: Nidhogg has taken his true form.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Heart Of Man: Nidhogg has taken the form of a man.
ContentDesc_Der letzte Schicksalsweg: Imbued with Hraesvelgr's last sliver of hope, you stand at the forefront of your allies as the last bastion against the raging shade of Nidhogg. Have you the resolve to conquer the great wyrm at the height of his power, or will Ishgard perish in fire and ruin? Here, on the battle-stricken Steps of Faith, your deeds shall decide how the final verse of a thousand-year dirge of grief and vengeance will be sung.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_12600_Text: Wriggling maggots! I shall grind you to paste in my jaws!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_12601_Text: Come, my children! Claim the vengeance that is rightfully yours!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_12602_Text: Look upon the fool who dared embrace my power! Witness the darkened wings that beat about his shriveled soul!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_12603_Text: Champions of man! Hearken to my fury!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_12605_Text: Brood-brother, thou hast doomed me... But if I must meet mine end, then all shall burn upon my pyre!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_12608_Text: Thou hast survived my song... Curse thee and thine eye, Hraesvelgr!
